 a\ntraffic model using our captures. We show that this model can be used in\nsimulations to further investigate the network performance in presence of\nStadia traffic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2020 12:06:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 May 2022 11:17:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-24"}
