re\nthan 95% over the four common types of DeepFakes. Our research finding confirms\neffective privacy-preserving techniques for protecting personal photos from\nbeing DeepFaked.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2020 13:41:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Jul 2021 12:13:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 26 Sep 2021 11:45:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-28"}
